---
title: Lemony Panko-Crusted Chicken with Sweet Potatoes and Creamy Dill Sauce
description: Coat tender chicken thighs with a zesty crumb for a dinner that's sure to please. With sweet potato wedges, fresh salad, a tangy mustard dressing, and a creamy dill sauce for dipping, this meal is the best of the best!
